w to Use</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"16\" data-end=\"324\">You can schedule cultural exchange sessions through the Global Zone reservation system provided by the Center for International Affairs, and participate in the activities via ZOOM at your reserved time.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"16\" data-end=\"324\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-start=\"16\" data-end=\"324\">Global Zone Reservation System URL: <a class=\"\" href=\"https://gzone.yju.ac.kr\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"257\" data-end=\"280\" data-is-only-node=\"\">https://gzone.yju.ac.kr</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"16\" data-end=\"324\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"16\" data-end=\"324\">Please follow the usage guidelines below:</p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"326\" data-end=\"873\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">\r\n<li data-start=\"326\" data-end=\"405\">\r\n<p data-start=\"328\" data-end=\"405\">Each session lasts 20 minutes, with a maximum of 4 participants per session</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"406\" data-end=\"489\">\r\n<p data-start=\"408\" data-end=\"489\">Maximum 3 sessions per person per day, and up to 6 sessions per person per week</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"490\" data-end=\"783\">\r\n<p data-start=\"492\" data-end=\"783\">When signing up for the Global Zone reservation system, you must use your school Google Gmail account.<br data-start=\"594\" data-end=\"597\">If you do not have a school Gmail account, please refer to the website below to create one first, and then proceed with registration (Guide to Creating Yeungjin Google Gmail Account)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"784\" data-end=\"873\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\n<p data-start=\"786\" data-end=\"873\" data-is-last-node=\"\">When using a PC to make a reservation, it is recommended to use the Chrome web browser.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,'globalPrograms','english','2025-06-13 10:38:57.524195','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(212,'globalcenterEnglish','<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong>Global Center</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 101.183%; height: 221.39px; border-width: 0px; border-style: hidden;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 55.6385%;\"><col style=\"width: 1.7413%;\"><col style=\"width: 42.6203%;\"></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 221.39px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 221.39px; border-width: 0px;\"><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/8a14f5ce-eaca-4707-86b5-df7f1120fea6-.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"629\" height=\"408\"></td>\r\n<td style=\"border-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 221.39px; border-style: none; border-width: 0px;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"30\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"30\">What is the Global Center?</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"32\" data-end=\"289\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">\r\n<li data-start=\"32\" data-end=\"204\">\r\n<p data-start=\"34\" data-end=\"204\">A place for English-related extracurricular activities such as English conversation with professors from English-speaking countries and English r&eacute;sum&eacute; (CV) proofreading</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"205\" data-end=\"261\">\r\n<p data-start=\"207\" data-end=\"261\">Activities available as group or one-on-one sessions</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"262\" data-end=\"289\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\n<p data-start=\"264\" data-end=\"289\" data-is-last-node=\"\">Location: Online via ZOOM</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"border-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"border-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"border-style: none; border-width: 0px;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"border-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"border-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"border-style: none; border-width: 0px;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"14\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"14\">How to Use</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"16\" data-end=\"333\">You can schedule exchange sessions through the Global Zone reservation system provided by the Center for International Affairs, and participate in the cultural exchange activities via ZOOM at your reserved time.<br data-start=\"227\" data-end=\"230\">Global Zone Reservation System URL: <a class=\"\" href=\"https://gzone.yju.ac.kr\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"266\" data-end=\"289\" data-is-only-node=\"\">https://gzone.yju.ac.kr</a><br data-start=\"289\" data-end=\"292\">Please follow the usage guidelines below:</p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"335\" data-end=\"850\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">\r\n<li data-start=\"335\" data-end=\"407\">\r\n<p data-start=\"337\" data-end=\"407\">Each session lasts 20 minutes, with up to 4 participants per session</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"408\" data-end=\"494\">\r\n<p data-start=\"410\" data-end=\"494\">Maximum of 3 sessions per person per day, and up to 6 sessions per person per week</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"495\" data-end=\"771\">\r\n<p data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"771\">When registering for the Global Zone reservation system, you must use your school Google Gmail account.<br data-start=\"600\" data-end=\"603\">If you do not have a school Gmail account, please refer to the site below to create one before registering<br data-start=\"711\" data-end=\"714\" data-is-only-node=\"\"><em data-start=\"716\" data-end=\"769\">(Guide to creating a Yeungjin Google Gmail account)</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"772\" data-end=\"850\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\n<p data-start=\"774\" data-end=\"850\" data-is-last-node=\"\">When making a reservation using a PC, the Chrome web browser is recommended.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1,'globalPrograms','english','2025-06-13 10:40:25.058963','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(213,'globalzoneJapanese','<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong>グローバルゾーン</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100.008%; height: 221.39px; border-width: 0px; border-style: hidden;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 63.1717%;\"><col style=\"width: 5.62092%;\"><col style=\"width: 31.2083%;\"></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 221.39px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 221.39px; border-width: 0px;\"><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/01990f28-bc9f-4fa3-8b13-e5f8cb7d461c-1-ab198932.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"740\" height=\"362\"></td>\r\n<td style=\"border-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 221.39px; border-style: none; border-width: 0px;\">\r\n<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"31\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"29\">グローバル・ゾーン（Global Zone）とは？</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"32\" data-end=\"95\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">\r\n<li data-start=\"32\" data-end=\"57\">\r\n<p data-start=\"34\" data-end=\"57\">留学生との外国語を使った国際文化交流を実施</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"58\" data-end=\"74\">\r\n<p data-start=\"60\" data-end=\"74\">使用言語：日本語、中国語</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"75\" data-end=\"95\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\n<p data-start=\"77\" data-end=\"95\" data-is-last-node=\"\">実施場所：オンライン（ZOOM利用）</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"10\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"10\">■ 利用方法</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"12\" data-end=\"152\">国際交流院のグローバル・ゾーン予約システムを利用して交流日程を予約し、予約した時間にZOOMを通じて文化交流活動を行うことができます。<br data-start=\"79\" data-end=\"82\">グローバル・ゾーン予約システムURL： <a class=\"\" href=\"https://gzone.yju.ac.kr\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"102\" data-end=\"152\">https://gzone.yju.ac.kr</a></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"154\" data-end=\"173\">以下の利用規則を守ってご利用ください：</p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"175\" data-end=\"230\">\r\n<li data-start=\"175\" data-end=\"196\">\r\n<p data-start=\"177\" data-end=\"196\">1回20分、1回あたり最大4人まで</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"197\" data-end=\"230\">\r\n<p data-start=\"199\" data-end=\"230\">1人1日3回まで利用可能、1人1週間で最大6回まで利用可能</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"232\" data-end=\"376\">グローバル・ゾーン予約システムに会員登録する際は、学校のGoogle Gmailアカウントを使用してください。<br data-start=\"287\" data-end=\"290\">学校のGmailアカウントをお持ちでない場合は、下記のサイトを参考にまずアカウントを作成してからご登録ください（ヨンジンGoogle Gmailアカウント作成ガイド）。</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"378\" data-end=\"410\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">PCで予約を行う場合は、Chromeブラウザの使用を推奨します。</p>',1,'globalPrograms','korean','2025-06-13 10:41:38.835861','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(214,'globalcenterJapanese','<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong>グローバルセンター</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 101.183%; height: 221.39px; border-width: 0px; border-style: hidden;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 55.6385%;\"><col style=\"width: 1.7413%;\"><col style=\"width: 42.6203%;\"></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 221.39px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 221.39px; border-width: 0px;\"><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/8a14f5ce-eaca-4707-86b5-df7f1120fea6-.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"629\" height=\"408\"></td>\r\n<td style=\"border-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 221.39px; border-style: none; border-width: 0px;\">\r\n<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"34\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"32\">グローバル・センター（Global Center）とは？</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"36\" data-end=\"119\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">\r\n<li data-start=\"36\" data-end=\"79\">\r\n<p data-start=\"38\" data-end=\"79\">英語圏の教授との英会話や英文履歴書の添削など、英語に関する課外の特別活動を実施</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"80\" data-end=\"98\">\r\n<p data-start=\"82\" data-end=\"98\">グループまたは個別指導を実施</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"99\" data-end=\"119\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\r\n<p data-start=\"101\" data-end=\"119\" data-is-last-node=\"\">実施場所：オンライン（ZOOM利用）</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"border-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"border-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"border-style: none; border-width: 0px;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"border-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"border-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"border-style: none; border-width: 0px;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"10\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"10\">■ 利用方法</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"12\" data-end=\"152\">国際交流院のグローバル・ゾーン予約システムを利用して交流日程を予約し、予約した時間にZOOMを通じて文化交流活動を行うことができます。<br data-start=\"79\" data-end=\"82\">グローバル・ゾーン予約システムURL： <a class=\"\" href=\"https://gzone.yju.ac.kr\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"102\" data-end=\"152\">https://gzone.yju.ac.kr</a></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"154\" data-end=\"173\">以下の利用規則を守ってご利用ください：</p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"175\" data-end=\"226\">\r\n<li data-start=\"175\" data-end=\"196\">\r\n<p data-start=\"177\" data-end=\"196\">1回20分、1回あたり最大4名まで</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"197\" data-end=\"226\">\r\n<p data-start=\"199\" data-end=\"226\">1人1日3回まで、1人1週間で最大6回まで利用可能</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"228\" data-end=\"376\">グローバル・ゾーン予約システムに会員登録する際は、学校のGoogle Gmailアカウントを使用してください。<br data-start=\"283\" data-end=\"286\">学校のGmailアカウントをお持ちでない場合は、下記のサイトを参考にまずアカウントを作成し、その後登録を進めてください（ヨンジンGoogle Gmailアカウント作成ガイド）。</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"378\" data-end=\"415\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">パソコンで予約を行う場合は、Chromeウェブブラウザの使用を推奨します。</p>',1,'globalPrograms','korean','2025-06-13 10:43:34.675486','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(215,'2024年 外国人留学生 韓国語スピーチ大会 案内','<p data-start=\"428\" data-end=\"530\">国際交流院では、外国人留学生のグローバルマインドの育成および韓国語能力の向上を目的として、<br data-start=\"487\" data-end=\"490\">「2024年 外国人留学生 韓国語スピーチ大会」を下記の通り実施いたします。</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"532\" data-end=\"576\">多くの学生が参加できるよう、教職員の皆様のご関心とご指導をよろしくお願いいたします。</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"578\" data-end=\"592\"><strong data-start=\"578\" data-end=\"592\">行事案内ポスター添付</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/c390186e-8455-4fe7-872f-75fc4229b503-20240509_154728097_93729.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"585\" height=\"845\"></strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"826\" data-end=\"842\"><strong data-start=\"826\" data-end=\"840\">2. 概要および目的</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"843\" data-end=\"919\">\r\n<li data-start=\"843\" data-end=\"871\">\r\n<p data-start=\"845\" data-end=\"871\">韓国語学習への動機づけおよび韓国語運用能力の向上</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"872\" data-end=\"919\">\r\n<p data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"919\">韓国文化への理解を深め、自国の文化と歴史を紹介する場を設け、多様な文化体験の機会を提供</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"921\" data-end=\"941\"><strong data-start=\"921\" data-end=\"939\">3. 主な内容および実施日程</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"942\" data-end=\"1104\">\r\n<li data-start=\"942\" data-end=\"979\">\r\n<p data-start=\"944\" data-end=\"979\"><strong data-start=\"944\" data-end=\"952\">開催日時</strong>：2024年5月24日（金）15:00～17:00</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"980\" data-end=\"1005\">\r\n<p data-start=\"982\" data-end=\"1005\"><strong data-start=\"982\" data-end=\"990\">実施方法</strong>：対面（オフライン）で実施</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1006\" data-end=\"1034\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1008\" data-end=\"1034\"><strong data-start=\"1008\" data-end=\"1016\">参加対象</strong>：ヨンジン専門大学の外国人留学生</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1035\" data-end=\"1051\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1037\" data-end=\"1051\"><strong data-start=\"1037\" data-end=\"1045\">使用言語</strong>：韓国語</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1052\" data-end=\"1075\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1054\" data-end=\"1075\"><strong data-start=\"1054\" data-end=\"1062\">選考方式</strong>：予選および本選の審査</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1076\" data-end=\"1104\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1078\" data-end=\"1104\"><strong data-start=\"1078\" data-end=\"1086\">表彰特典</strong>：総長名義の賞状および賞品を授与</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"1106\" data-end=\"1120\"><strong data-start=\"1106\" data-end=\"1118\">4. 発表テーマ</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1121\" data-end=\"1169\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1121\" data-end=\"1129\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1123\" data-end=\"1129\">自由発表</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1130\" data-end=\"1143\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1132\" data-end=\"1143\">発表時間：5分以内</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1144\" data-end=\"1169\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1146\" data-end=\"1169\">PowerPointスライド：3～5枚程度</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,'notice','japanese','2025-06-13 10:49:34.953390','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(216,'2024 Korean Speaking Contest for International Students – Event Information','<p data-start=\"35\" data-end=\"276\">The Center for International Affairs will be hosting the &ldquo;2024 Korean Speaking Contest for International Students&rdquo;<br data-start=\"162\" data-end=\"165\">with the aim of fostering a global mindset and enhancing Korean language skills among international students.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"278\" data-end=\"394\">We kindly ask for the attention and guidance of faculty and staff to encourage active participation from students.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"396\" data-end=\"421\"><strong data-start=\"396\" data-end=\"421\">Event Poster Attached</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/c390186e-8455-4fe7-872f-75fc4229b503-20240509_154728097_93729.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"585\" height=\"845\"></strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"51\" data-end=\"80\"><strong data-start=\"51\" data-end=\"78\">2. Overview and Purpose</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"81\" data-end=\"320\">\r\n<li data-start=\"81\" data-end=\"165\">\r\n<p data-start=\"83\" data-end=\"165\">To motivate students in learning Korean and improve their Korean language skills</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"166\" data-end=\"320\">\r\n<p data-start=\"168\" data-end=\"320\">To enhance understanding of Korean culture and provide opportunities to introduce their own culture and history, offering diverse cultural experiences</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"322\" data-end=\"356\"><strong data-start=\"322\" data-end=\"354\">3. Main Details and Schedule</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"357\" data-end=\"696\">\r\n<li data-start=\"357\" data-end=\"420\">\r\n<p data-start=\"359\" data-end=\"420\"><strong data-start=\"359\" data-end=\"380\">Event Date &amp; Time</strong>: May 24, 2024 (Friday), 15:00 ~ 17:00</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"421\" data-end=\"462\">\r\n<p data-start=\"423\" data-end=\"462\"><strong data-start=\"423\" data-end=\"439\">Event Format</strong>: Offline (in-person)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"463\" data-end=\"527\">\r\n<p data-start=\"465\" data-end=\"527\"><strong data-start=\"465\" data-end=\"481\">Participants</strong>: International students of Yeungjin College</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"528\" data-end=\"557\">\r\n<p data-start=\"530\" data-end=\"557\"><strong data-start=\"530\" data-end=\"547\">Language Used</strong>: Korean</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"558\" data-end=\"627\">\r\n<p data-start=\"560\" data-end=\"627\"><strong data-start=\"560\" data-end=\"581\">Selection Process</strong>: Preliminary and final rounds of evaluation</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"628\" data-end=\"696\">\r\n<p data-start=\"630\" data-end=\"696\"><strong data-start=\"630\" data-end=\"640\">Awards</strong>: Certificates in the name of the President and prizes</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"725\"><strong data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"723\">4. Presentation Topic</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"726\" data-end=\"803\">\r\n<li data-start=\"726\" data-end=\"740\">\r\n<p data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"740\">Free topic</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"741\" data-end=\"774\">\r\n<p data-start=\"743\" data-end=\"774\">Presentation within 5 minutes</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"775\" data-end=\"803\">\r\n<p data-start=\"777\" data-end=\"803\">3 to 5 PowerPoint slides</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,'notice','english','2025-06-13 10:49:40.677687','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(217,'2025年 外国人留学生 韓国語スピーチ大会 案内','<p><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/c3991484-a934-4130-b83b-65ee3d0de423-20250425_171236062_33862.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"891\" height=\"1260\"></p>',1,'notice','japanese','2025-06-13 10:50:24.608137','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(218,'2025 Korean Speaking Contest for International Students – Information','<p><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/c3991484-a934-4130-b83b-65ee3d0de423-20250425_171236062_33862.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"891\" height=\"1260\"></p>',1,'notice','english','2025-06-13 10:50:27.579806','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(219,'2025年 YJU外国語プレゼンテーション大会 案内','<p><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/065fe64c-08bc-4b07-a27b-111ceb705e50-20250424_164420059_78012.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"926\" height=\"1316\"></p>',1,'notice','japanese','2025-06-13 10:51:06.600577','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(220,'2025 YJU Foreign Language Presentation Contest – Information','<p><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/065fe64c-08bc-4b07-a27b-111ceb705e50-20250424_164420059_78012.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"926\" height=\"1316\"></p>',1,'notice','english','2025-06-13 10:51:08.629553','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(221,'2025 Yeungjin Buddy (BUDDY) Program – Participation Guide','<p><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/58abea54-1b9f-446f-9ce9-f5899595ec76-20250422_174555661_79913.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"926\" height=\"1310\"></p>',1,'notice','english','2025-06-13 10:51:54.942677','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(222,'2025年 ヨンジン バディ（BUDDY）プログラム 参加案内','<p><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/58abea54-1b9f-446f-9ce9-f5899595ec76-20250422_174555661_79913.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"926\" height=\"1310\"></p>',1,'notice','japanese','2025-06-13 10:51:57.630894','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(223,'2025 Spring Semester Global Zone/Center Operation Guide','<p><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/fa063b48-1ae2-4109-a5e2-ea1d7561c6b6-20250401_144006247_08856.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"926\" height=\"1310\"></p>',1,'notice','english','2025-06-13 11:07:07.093939','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(224,'2025年度 第1学期 グローバル・ゾーン／センター運営案内','<p><img src=\"https://oic.yju.ac.kr/api/files//post-image/fa063b48-1ae2-4109-a5e2-ea1d7561c6b6-20250401_144006247_08856.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"926\" height=\"1310\"></p>',1,'notice','japanese','2025-06-13 11:07:11.611729','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(225,'Student Support Services','<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\"><strong>Operation of the Dedicated International Student Support Team</strong></span></p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-start=\"79\" data-end=\"205\">\r\n<p data-start=\"82\" data-end=\"205\">A dedicated team is in operation to support international students with admission, academics, daily life, and graduation.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"206\" data-end=\"349\">\r\n<p data-start=\"209\" data-end=\"349\">The office is located in Room 115 of the Main Building and is staffed by three dedicated employees who are fluent in English and Japanese.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"350\" data-end=\"626\">\r\n<p data-start=\"353\" data-end=\"626\">The team provides support for essential daily needs such as alien registration and opening a bank account after arrival, as well as one-on-one assistance with academic and life-related matters such as classes, grades, temporary return to home country, and visa extension.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"810\">\r\n<p data-start=\"630\" data-end=\"810\">For inquiries related to academics and life in Korea&mdash;such as class registration, grades, temporary leave, and visa extension&mdash;the dedicated team provides personalized 1:1 support.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"811\" data-end=\"1049\">\r\n<p data-start=\"814\" data-end=\"1049\">There&rsquo;s no need to worry about studying abroad in Korea. The international student support team at Yeungjin College will take care of your needs with great attention and will do their best to ensure a safe and comfortable student life.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\"><strong>International Student Support Services</strong></span></p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"80\" data-end=\"120\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"80\" data-end=\"120\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">Freshman Pickup Service Support</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"121\" data-end=\"472\">\r\n<li data-start=\"121\" data-end=\"281\">\r\n<p data-start=\"124\" data-end=\"281\">When international students staying in the dormitory arrive at the Bokhyeon Campus East Gate, a staff member from the school will provide a pickup service.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"282\" data-end=\"389\">\r\n<p data-start=\"285\" data-end=\"389\">After moving to the dormitory with the staff, an orientation will be held on how to use the dormitory.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"390\" data-end=\"472\">\r\n<p data-start=\"393\" data-end=\"472\">This helps students begin their first day in Korea with comfort and confidence.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"479\" data-end=\"508\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">Freshman Orientation</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"509\" data-end=\"840\">\r\n<li data-start=\"509\" data-end=\"594\">\r\n<p data-start=\"512\" data-end=\"594\">Detailed guidance is provided on the academic calendar and general student life.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"595\" data-end=\"693\">\r\n<p data-start=\"598\" data-end=\"693\">Students will also walk around and explore the beautiful campus of Yeungjin College together.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"694\" data-end=\"840\">\r\n<p data-start=\"697\" data-end=\"840\">In addition to detailed information on course registration, students will be introduced to important nearby facilities and popular restaurants.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"847\" data-end=\"905\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"847\" data-end=\"905\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">Bank Account Opening &amp; Alien Registration Support</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"906\" data-end=\"1234\">\r\n<li data-start=\"906\" data-end=\"1004\">\r\n<p data-start=\"909\" data-end=\"1004\">Worried about opening a bank account or applying for an Alien Registration Card? Don&rsquo;t worry!</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1005\" data-end=\"1093\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1008\" data-end=\"1093\">Our team will accompany you to the bank and help with all the necessary procedures.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1094\" data-end=\"1234\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1097\" data-end=\"1234\">Even if you&rsquo;re unfamiliar with Korean or complex administrative steps, the Center for International Affairs is here to fully support you.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1241\" data-end=\"1274\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1241\" data-end=\"1274\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">New Semester Orientation</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"1275\" data-end=\"1560\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1275\" data-end=\"1394\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1278\" data-end=\"1394\">As the new semester begins, detailed information will be provided on academic schedules and various school events.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1395\" data-end=\"1560\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1398\" data-end=\"1560\">This includes exam schedules (midterms and finals), as well as the Buddy Program and other campus activities that will support both your academic and social life.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1567\" data-end=\"1600\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1567\" data-end=\"1600\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">End-of-Semester Ceremony</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"1601\" data-end=\"1866\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1601\" data-end=\"1729\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1604\" data-end=\"1729\">After the semester ends, information will be provided on how to check your grades and complete temporary return procedures.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1730\" data-end=\"1866\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1733\" data-end=\"1866\">Additionally, details about free Korean language classes during vacations and special activities with Korean students will be shared.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1873\" data-end=\"1917\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1873\" data-end=\"1917\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">TOPIK Application Process &amp; Support</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"1918\" data-end=\"2121\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1918\" data-end=\"2028\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1921\" data-end=\"2028\">Notifications and guidance will be provided on registering for the TOPIK (Test of Proficiency in Korean).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2029\" data-end=\"2121\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2032\" data-end=\"2121\">Let&rsquo;s aim to achieve Level 6 before graduation and support each other to reach that goal!</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\"><strong>Academic Support</strong></span></p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"86\" data-end=\"149\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">Free Korean Language Classes During Semester and Vacation</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"150\" data-end=\"422\">\r\n<li data-start=\"150\" data-end=\"237\">\r\n<p data-start=\"153\" data-end=\"237\">Free Korean language classes are offered during the semester and vacation periods.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"238\" data-end=\"422\">\r\n<p data-start=\"241\" data-end=\"422\">Classes are divided by TOPIK levels (Level 2 to 6), and various programs are operated to help international students improve their Korean skills. Participation is highly encouraged.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"424\" data-end=\"464\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">Buddy Program with Korean Students</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"465\" data-end=\"883\">\r\n<li data-start=\"465\" data-end=\"602\">\r\n<p data-start=\"468\" data-end=\"602\">A buddy program with Korean students is offered to help international students enjoy a more comfortable and enjoyable life in Korea.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"603\" data-end=\"803\">\r\n<p data-start=\"606\" data-end=\"803\">By teaming up with Korean students, participants can receive practical assistance with daily life in Korea and gain deeper understanding of Korean culture through international cultural exchange.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"804\" data-end=\"883\">\r\n<p data-start=\"807\" data-end=\"883\">These experiences will make your life in Korea more enjoyable and rewarding.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>',1,'student-support','english','2025-06-13 11:46:11.758029','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(226,'学生支援サービス','<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\"><strong>留学生支援専任運営チームの運営</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-start=\"1096\" data-end=\"1135\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1135\">留学生の入学、学業、生活、卒業を支援する専任チームを運営しています。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1136\" data-end=\"1187\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1139\" data-end=\"1187\">本館115号室の国際交流院に位置しており、英語と日本語に堪能な専任職員3名が常駐しています。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1188\" data-end=\"1279\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1191\" data-end=\"1279\">入国後の外国人登録証の発給や銀行口座の開設など、基本的な生活支援はもちろん、授業、成績、一時帰国、ビザ延長など、学業および生活に関する問い合わせにも1対1で対応しています。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1280\" data-end=\"1350\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1283\" data-end=\"1350\">学業および韓国での生活（授業、成績、一時帰国、ビザ延長など）に関する質問がある場合、専任運営チームが1対1で丁寧に対応しています。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1351\" data-end=\"1440\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1354\" data-end=\"1440\">韓国での留学生活に不安を感じる必要はありません。ヨンジン専門大学の留学生支援専任チームが皆さんのニーズに細かく対応し、安全で快適な留学生活を送れるよう全力でサポートします。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\"><strong>留学生支援内容</strong></span></p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2167\" data-end=\"2191\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">新入生ピックアップサービス支援</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"2192\" data-end=\"2349\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2192\" data-end=\"2257\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2195\" data-end=\"2257\">寮に入居する留学生が福賢（ボッキョン）キャンパス東門に到着すると、本校の担当スタッフがピックアップサービスを提供します。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2258\" data-end=\"2307\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2261\" data-end=\"2307\">スタッフと一緒に寮へ移動した後は、寮の利用方法についてのオリエンテーションを実施します。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2308\" data-end=\"2349\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2311\" data-end=\"2349\">これにより、留学生が韓国での初日を安心してスタートできるようサポートします。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2356\" data-end=\"2377\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">新入生オリエンテーション</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"2378\" data-end=\"2488\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2378\" data-end=\"2405\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2381\" data-end=\"2405\">学事日程や生活全般について詳しく案内します。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2406\" data-end=\"2443\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2409\" data-end=\"2443\">ヨンジン専門大学の美しいキャンパスを一緒に歩きながら紹介します。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2444\" data-end=\"2488\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2447\" data-end=\"2488\">履修登録の具体的な案内はもちろん、学校周辺の重要な施設や人気の飲食店も紹介します。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2495\" data-end=\"2523\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">銀行口座開設・外国人登録証申請サポート</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"2524\" data-end=\"2651\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2524\" data-end=\"2563\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2527\" data-end=\"2563\">銀行口座の開設や外国人登録証の申請が心配ですか？ご安心ください！^^</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2564\" data-end=\"2604\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2567\" data-end=\"2604\">私たちのチームが銀行まで同行し、必要なすべての手続きをサポートします。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2605\" data-end=\"2651\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2608\" data-end=\"2651\">韓国語や複雑な行政手続きに慣れていなくても大丈夫。国際交流院が全面的にサポートします。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2658\" data-end=\"2682\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">新学期オリエンテーションの実施</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"2683\" data-end=\"2794\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2683\" data-end=\"2731\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2686\" data-end=\"2731\">新学期が始まるにあたり、学事日程やさまざまな学校行事についての詳しい情報を提供します。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2732\" data-end=\"2794\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2735\" data-end=\"2794\">特に中間・期末試験の日程や、韓国人学生と一緒に参加するバディプログラムなど、キャンパス生活に役立つ情報をお伝えします。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2801\" data-end=\"2822\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">学期終了セレモニーの実施</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"2823\" data-end=\"2919\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2823\" data-end=\"2865\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2826\" data-end=\"2865\">学期終了後、成績確認の方法や一時帰国に関する行政手続きについて案内します。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2866\" data-end=\"2919\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2869\" data-end=\"2919\">また、休暇中の無料韓国語特別講座のスケジュールや、韓国人学生との特別活動についての情報も提供します。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2926\" data-end=\"2950\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">TOPIK申請手続き案内と支援</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"2951\" data-end=\"3033\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2951\" data-end=\"2997\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2954\" data-end=\"2997\">韓国語能力試験（TOPIK）の申請に関する案内と、申請手続きのサポートを行います。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2998\" data-end=\"3033\">\r\n<p data-start=\"3001\" data-end=\"3033\">卒業までにTOPIK6級の取得を目指して、一緒に頑張りましょう！</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\"><strong>学業関連支援</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"929\" data-end=\"954\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">学期・休暇中の無料韓国語特別講座の運営</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"955\" data-end=\"1076\">\r\n<li data-start=\"955\" data-end=\"989\">\r\n<p data-start=\"958\" data-end=\"989\">学期中および休暇中に無料の韓国語特別講座を提供しています。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"990\" data-end=\"1076\">\r\n<p data-start=\"993\" data-end=\"1076\">TOPIKの2級から6級までレベル別にクラスが分かれており、留学生の韓国語能力向上を目的とした多様なプログラムを無料で運営しています。多くのご参加をお待ちしています。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1078\" data-end=\"1102\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161);\">韓国人学生とのバディプログラムの運営</span></h3>\r\n<ol data-start=\"1103\" data-end=\"1292\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1103\" data-end=\"1155\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1106\" data-end=\"1155\">韓国での生活をより楽しく、快適に過ごすために、韓国人学生とのバディプログラムを実施しています。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1156\" data-end=\"1244\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1159\" data-end=\"1244\">韓国人学生とチームを組むことで、実際の生活に役立つサポートを受けられるだけでなく、国際文化交流を通じてさまざまな文化を体験し、韓国に対する理解を深めることができます。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1245\" data-end=\"1292\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1248\" data-end=\"1292\">これらの経験は、皆さんの韓国での生活をより楽しく、充実したものにしてくれることでしょう。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>',1,'student-support','japanese','2025-06-13 11:46:13.496011','2025-06-16 01:41:24.433232'),(227,'グローバル現場学習','<p><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong>グローバル現場学習とは？</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>アメリカ、イギリス、オーストラリア、日本、中国などの海外現地で語学研修および現場実習を実施します。</li>\r\n<li>語学研修2ヶ月＋インターンシップ2ヶ月、合計4ヶ月間の海外派遣プログラムです。</li>\r\n<li>食費および個人生活費を除くすべての費用は、国費および大学費用で支援されます。つまり、無料で海外派遣が受けられます！</li>\r\n<li>主管：大韓民国教育部、韓国専門大学協議会、ヨンジン専門大学</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\">応募資格</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100.597%; height: 412px; border-width: 1px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 8.31218%;\"><col style=\"width: 35.5498%;\"><col style=\"width: 56.1068%;\"></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3906px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 22.3906px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">条件</span></strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 22.3906px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一般選考</span></strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 22.3906px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">オープン選考</span></strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3906px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 22.3906px; border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">在籍</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 22.3906px; border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\" colspan=\"2\">&nbsp;応募日時点で2学期以上修了した在学生（派遣予定時も在学生であること）</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3906px;\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">成績</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>累積GPAが4.5満点中3.0以上（B0相当）</p>\r\n<p>の在学生（復学予定者を含む）</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-3\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\">&nbsp; 제한 없음</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3906px;\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">語学</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>本事業の遂行に必要な一定基準以上の</p>\r\n<p>語学能力証明書を提出できる者</p>\r\n<p>（下記の表を参照）</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-3\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\">&nbsp;派遣者確定時までに提出可能であれば応募可</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3906px;\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">\r\n<p>その他</p>\r\n<p>の条件</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-start=\"1624\" data-end=\"1656\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1626\" data-end=\"1656\">ビザ取得など、グローバル現場学習への参加に支障がないこと</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1659\" data-end=\"1680\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1661\" data-end=\"1680\">人格、健康、身元等に問題がないこと</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1683\" data-end=\"1703\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1685\" data-end=\"1703\">外国籍および二重国籍者は参加不可</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1706\" data-end=\"1749\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1708\" data-end=\"1749\">事業参加年度終了後3年間の個人情報（就職先、就職情報など）の提供に同意できる者</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1752\" data-end=\"1773\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1754\" data-end=\"1773\">同一人物による本事業の再参加は不可</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1776\" data-end=\"1816\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1778\" data-end=\"1816\">同年度中に政府または地方自治体が実施する類似インターン事業との重複参加は不可</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">語学</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100.672%; height: 755.604px; border-width: 1px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 29.6316%;\"><col style=\"width: 38.7674%;\"><col style=\"width: 31.5287%;\"></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 26.125px;\">\r\n<th class=\"column-1\" style=\"height: 26.125px; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt;\">조건</span></th>\r\n<th class=\"column-2\" style=\"height: 26.125px; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt;\">語学試験の種類および基準スコア</span></th>\r\n<th class=\"column-3\" style=\"height: 26.125px; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt;\">備考</span></th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 300.75px;\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\" style=\"height: 300.75px; border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">英語</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\" style=\"height: 300.75px; border-width: 1px;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-start=\"411\" data-end=\"425\">\r\n<p data-start=\"413\" data-end=\"425\">TOEIC：550点</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"426\" data-end=\"443\">\r\n<p data-start=\"428\" data-end=\"443\">G-TELP 2級：42点</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"444\" data-end=\"458\">\r\n<p data-start=\"446\" data-end=\"458\">OPIc：NHレベル</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"459\" data-end=\"485\">\r\n<p data-start=\"461\" data-end=\"485\">TOEICスピーキング：レベル5（110点）</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"486\" data-end=\"499\">\r\n<p data-start=\"488\" data-end=\"499\">TEPS：450点</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"500\" data-end=\"511\">\r\n<p data-start=\"502\" data-end=\"511\">ESPT：3級</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"512\" data-end=\"547\">\r\n<p data-start=\"514\" data-end=\"547\">TOEFL：PBT 450点、CBT 137点、IBT 55点</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"548\" data-end=\"565\">\r\n<p data-start=\"550\" data-end=\"565\">TOSEL（A）：397点</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"566\" data-end=\"579\">\r\n<p data-start=\"568\" data-end=\"579\">TESL：104点</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"580\" data-end=\"592\">\r\n<p data-start=\"582\" data-end=\"592\">IELTS：4.5点</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-3\" style=\"height: 729.479px; border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"4\">\r\n<p>語学試験のスコアは、申請締切日を</p>\r\n<p>基準に過去2年以内に発行されたもののみ有効です。</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 73.583px;\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\" style=\"height: 73.583px; border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">ドイツ語</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\" style=\"height: 73.583px; border-width: 1px;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-start=\"191\" data-end=\"214\">\r\n<p data-start=\"193\" data-end=\"214\">ゲーテ・インスティトゥート：A2レベル</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"215\" data-end=\"231\">\r\n<p data-start=\"217\" data-end=\"231\">TestDaF：TDN3以上</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 188.771px;\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\" style=\"height: 188.771px; border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">日本語</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\" style=\"height: 188.771px; border-width: 1px;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-start=\"331\" data-end=\"343\">\r\n<p data-start=\"333\" data-end=\"343\">JPT：415点</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"344\" data-end=\"356\">\r\n<p data-start=\"346\" data-end=\"356\">JLPT 新N4</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"357\" data-end=\"370\">\r\n<p data-start=\"359\" data-end=\"370\">SJPT：レベル3</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"371\" data-end=\"405\">\r\n<p data-start=\"373\" data-end=\"405\">日本語能力認定試験（NAT-TEST）：450点以上（2級相当）</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 166.375px;\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\" style=\"height: 166.375px; border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">中国語</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\" style=\"height: 166.375px; border-width: 1px;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;新HSK 3級</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"306\" data-end=\"316\">TSC：レベル3</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"319\" data-end=\"329\">CPT：300点</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"332\" data-end=\"342\">BCT：2級以上</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"345\" data-end=\"370\">TOCFL（華語文能力測験）：A1（レベル1）以上</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1,'global-internships','japanese','2025-06-13 12:16:48.850751','2025-06-16 11:01:12.000000'),(228,'Global Field Training','<p><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong>What is Global Field Training?</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Language training and on-site internship programs are conducted in countries such as the United States, United Kingdom, Australia, Japan, and China.</li>\r\n<li>Students are dispatched overseas for a total of 4 months: 2 months of language training + 2 months of internship.</li>\r\n<li>All expenses, except for food and personal living costs, are covered by the government and the university. In other words, it\'s a free overseas program!</li>\r\n<li>Organized by: Ministry of Education of the Republic of Korea, Korea Council for University College Education, Yeungjin College</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\">Eligibility Requirements</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100.597%; height: 412px; border-width: 1px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 11.4619%;\"><col style=\"width: 41.5346%;\"><col style=\"width: 47.0058%;\"></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3906px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 22.3906px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Conditions</span></strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 22.3906px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">General Track</span></strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 22.3906px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Open Track</span></strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3906px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 22.3906px; border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">\r\n<p>Eligibility</p>\r\n<p>Criteria</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 22.3906px; border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<p>Must be an enrolled student who has completed at least two semesters by the date of application.</p>\r\n<p>(Must maintain student status at the time of overseas dispatch)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3906px;\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">\r\n<p>Academic</p>\r\n<p>Performance</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>Cumulative GPA of 3.0 or higher on a 4.5 scale</p>\r\n<p>(equivalent to B0)</p>\r\n<p>(Students returning from leave of absence are also eligible)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-3\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\">&nbsp; 제한 없음</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3906px;\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">\r\n<p>Language</p>\r\n<p>Proficiency</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>Must be able to submit a language proficiency certificate that meets the program requirements</p>\r\n<p>(see table below)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-3\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\">\r\n<p>Language certificate may be submitted by the final</p>\r\n<p>confirmation date of selected participants</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3906px;\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">\r\n<p>Other</p>\r\n<p>Requirements</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\" style=\"border-width: 1px; text-align: left;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-start=\"774\" data-end=\"875\">\r\n<p data-start=\"776\" data-end=\"875\">No disqualification factors regarding visa issuance or participation in the Global Field Training</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"878\" data-end=\"944\">\r\n<p data-start=\"880\" data-end=\"944\">No personal issues related to character, health, or background</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"947\" data-end=\"1023\">\r\n<p data-start=\"949\" data-end=\"1023\">Foreign nationals and individuals with dual citizenship are not eligible</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1026\" data-end=\"1157\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1028\" data-end=\"1157\">Must consent to the provision of personal information (employment status and employer) for three years after program completion</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1160\" data-end=\"1232\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1162\" data-end=\"1232\">Re-application to the same program by the same person is not allowed</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1235\" data-end=\"1348\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1237\" data-end=\"1348\">Cannot participate in other similar government- or local-government-funded internship programs in the same year</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">Language Proficiency</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100.672%; height: 554.562px; border-width: 1px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 29.6642%;\"><col style=\"width: 34.5598%;\"><col style=\"width: 35.7442%;\"></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 52.25px;\">\r\n<th class=\"column-1\" style=\"height: 52.25px; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Conditions</span></strong></span></span></th>\r\n<th class=\"column-2\" style=\"height: 52.25px; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt;\">Types of Language Test Scores and Required Minimum Scores</span></th>\r\n<th class=\"column-3\" style=\"height: 52.25px; background-color: rgb(35, 111, 161); border-width: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt;\">Remarks</span></th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 255.958px;\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\" style=\"height: 255.958px; border-width: 1px; text-align: center;\">English</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\" style=\"height: 255.958px; border-width: 1px;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li data-start=\"118\" data-end=\"139\">\r\n<p data-start=\"120\" data-end=\"139\">TOEIC: 550 points</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\